        "recommended_action": "SSVC: Act \u2014 on CISA KEV (due 2022-05-25), EPSS ~100%, public exploits exist. Patch immediately: OpenSSL \u2192 1.0.1g+; FileZilla Server \u2192 0.9.44+; Splunk Enterprise \u2192 6.0.3+; Siemens ELAN \u2192 8.3.3+. After patching, rotate all TLS private keys, reissue certs, and invalidate sessions. Apply ATT&CK mitigations M1050 (Exploit Protection) and M1048 (App Isolation).",
